{"tid":541277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬寧承認未能情理兼備　向清潔女工李婆婆道歉","createTime":"2018-01-26T09:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T09:37:07.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eb33f4a8dbc81d95004829a847d57ec93cd56506","tid":541277,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"萬寧承認未能情理兼備　向清潔女工李婆婆道歉<br />\n2018-01-26 HKT 17:00<br />\n<br />\n77歲萬寧前清潔女工李淑卿，去年在荃灣分店帶走一卷印花，翌日歸還，被控一項盜竊罪，今日在西九龍裁判法院被裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n萬寧發表聲明，對今次事件未有恰當處理，以致李婆婆經歷有關司法程序，對她造成不便和困擾向她致歉，公司已經通知李婆婆，希望可以親身向她道歉，並向她提供所需支援及協助。<br />\n<br />\n萬寧又表示，尊重法庭裁決，已就事件作內部檢討，意識到在報案前，未有酌情考慮各種因素，導致未能做到情理兼備，公司會汲取教訓，日後在處理同類事件時會加倍謹慎，並由管理層考慮每一宗個案後，才決定是否轉交警方跟進。　"},{"pid":"4318516a6ded66c1cf3984ed6ed5cfa4146885ec","tid":541277,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c423b01d4c3a14c43421bc94af22d65f072bc5da","tid":541277,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1377486-20180126.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1377486-20180126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PKFOq%2F3hdZkIocf411TDxMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=d2845fab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1377486-20180126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6a1dd733\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1377486-20180126.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"678331326a8dc06e179f4fa2acd108f0192150c7","tid":541277,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"法官話阿婆本身好撚可疑"},{"pid":"523527eeb41027d3867d456e2b8fa5952169b7db","tid":541277,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"678331326a8dc06e179f4fa2acd108f0192150c7","tid":541277,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislik